# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# RITMOL — Environment Variables
# Copy this file to .env.local and fill in your values.
# NEVER commit .env.local to version control.
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# Dropbox OAuth App Key (public client — PKCE flow, no secret required)
# Create an app at https://www.dropbox.com/developers/apps
# Set "Access type" to "App folder" and add your redirect URI under "OAuth 2 > Redirect URIs".
# The App Key is inlined into the production bundle by Vite and is visible to users.
# Rotate it immediately if it appears in a public repository or HAR export.
# See src/api/dropbox.js for the full residual threat model.
VITE_DROPBOX_APP_KEY=your_dropbox_app_key_here
